  "remarks": "JSC Voskresensky Aggregation Factory assembles anti-aircraft guided missiles, air-to-air and air-to-surface guided missiles, cruise missiles, high-explosive aerial bombs (FABs) and improved FABs with unified gliding and correction modules which transform free-falling Russian bombs into guided ones, to the benefit of the Russian military, including for use in Ukraine.",
